criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:
1. Symptoms of upper digestive tract for more than 6 months or 3 monthes（postprandial fullness, early satiation,epigastric pain, and epigastric burning）；
2. From March 2018 to June 2018 ，patient went to the Gastroenterology clinics of the second affiliated hospital of xi'an jiaotong university and xijing hospital,and received gastroscope and upper abdominal B ultrasound examination;
3. Older than 18;
4. Able to engage in oral informed consent and be willing to participate in this study.
Exclusion Criteria:
1. The patient's vital signs are not stable;
2. The gastroscope was not successful or incomplete
